data.description: Location Location Location!!! This lakefront, mid-century looking, rustic bungalow is located in a site-built only area in the very desirable neighborhood- Forest Lake Village! This home has a great floorplan for a lake home and for entertaining guests. There is a large great room with a wood burning fireplace and a large Family room. The great room is off of the kitchen and dining area and the family room has a half bath and is off of the carport. Great way to separate the kids from the adults and room for everyone to spread out. The family room would also make a great movie or game room! The master bedroom is on the lakefront side and features an ensuite bath and walk-in closet and sliding glass doors going out onto the lakefront deck! The home is a split bedroom floorplan and one of the guest bedrooms also has a lakefront view and there is a full bath between the 2 guest bedrooms. The kitchen is spacious with an open concept to the dining room, great room and outside deck. There is also a separate 10x10 heated/cooled office located by the deck with an outside entrance and it has a lakefront view! There are vaulted ceilings in the family room with skylights and sidelights next to the stone fireplace. Down at the lake there is a L-shaped max dock and 5 ft of water and beautiful homes all around! There is also a private neighborhood boat ramp. With a little TLC this would make a great family get-a-way or permanent home! The Sale History on Zillow, etc. is regarding the home next door 228A Pine Knoll not this home and home next door does not have any waterfront like this one. This home has not been sold since 1997.
